        <h1>
          Cuppa!
        </h1>
        <p>
          Cup of cofee with your friend!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper how">
  <div class="container cuppa-home">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12" id="how">
        <h1>
          How it works
        </h1>
        <p>
          Invite your friends to join you on Cuppa and create your own customized coffee pots. Cuppa will check if there is a matching pot and randomly invites you and your friend on a coffee date! You'll meet your friend on a date, time and location you both like and finally have that cuppa' coffee together!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper facts">
  <div class="container cuppa-home">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12" id="facts">
